OUR INTERNATIONAL CASTING AGENCY

Collaborates with customers around the world. Our clients are people endowed with creativity and the desire to show their ideas to the audience and demonstrate their value

We are a casting agency that has its own established base of actors and selects personnel for implementation in various projects

Recording for casting

Popular questions

How to order a casting from you?

All questions and suggestions regarding further cooperation with us, you can send us by email: digitalmedia2020@proton.me

Our managers will contact you shortly!

Who do you usually collaborate with?

First of all, our customers are creative people endowed with talent and the desire to show the world their products, to demonstrate its value. We work mainly with foreign customers: we carry out the selection of actors for various creatives, large-scale campaigns and local creative projects for social networks and online advertising. We work both with famous brands and with less eminent, but no less talented people!

How do you select projects?

We select the most interesting and promising projects that will bring our actors not only experience, but also impressions. The most important things for us to choose are reliability, theme, creativity. When we’re choosing the projects, we pay attention to safety: we check the customer for frequency of further cooperation. This is done through our insiders and with careful data collection. Almost any customer can contact us, it doesn’t matter whether he or she is known in the media production market or not. If we’re confident in him or her, we’re always ready to implement the proposed ideas!

Why do you cast actors with no experience

We’re sure that every person can unleash his acting abilities and creativity. Our goal is to give people a unique opportunity to try themselves in a new sphere and get an unforgettable experience! We believe that you don’t have to be a professional to be a demanded actor on the media content market.

Many customers prefer new, little-known faces to candidates with great acting experience. Our team will create comfortable conditions for your adaptation and the best experience, the main thing is to have a desire!

How much can I earn with you?

Your fee depends on the project you’re taken part in and the role you’re approved for. Your desire to develop in the acting sphere is also important, because our casting managers are always ready to select many interesting projects for you and help in compiling a portfolio based on the results of shootings. Our actors get on average $350-700 for a shooting and the opportunity for further cooperation with a fee of $1000. We offer these projects in the case of constant cooperation with us!

I'm afraid to act without experience. What to do?

The actors with different levels of experience can cooperate with our agency. Even if you have no experience, you can pass an online casting, with the help of which we’ll determine your creativity and select a suitable project in which you have the opportunity to open up.

Our task is also to create comfortable and available (understandable) conditions for everyone, even if you are not familiar with acting at all. We adhere to this when we’re conducting the casting. Before the candidate proceeds to the selection stage of auditions, the casting manager will explain to you all the details, answer all questions and give practical advice on how to get into the role and open up.

On behalf of our company, we also provide access to various trainings and acting courses when concluding the cooperation contract. We’re ready to support you at the beginning of your creative journey!

Can I apply if I have little or no previous acting experience?

Yes, you can. We consider all applications regardless of your experience. Our agency encourages people to try themselves in acting career and to develop. You can believe in yourself and start a creative career with our support!

Can I take part in the shooting if I am in another country?

Yes, of course. We’ll conduct an online casting for you. After successfully passing the selection and approval for any project, our agency will help you with the transfer, we’ll compensate for travel expenses to the city where the shooting will be (transport, including a round-trip flight), and we’ll also pay for accommodation during participation in the project for our actors. Our experienced managers are ready to provide you with travel support on an individual basis.

How do we confirm our cooperation?

Our agency compulsorily concludes an agreement (electronic and before the shootings) with every candidate, it doesn’t matter whether it’s a one-time or long-term cooperation. We consider this an obligatory stage before fruitful cooperation, where both parties will be confident in their rights and safety.

All questions and suggestions regarding further cooperation with us, you can send us by email: digitalmedia2020@proton.me

Our managers will contact you shortly!
